  "body": "Description:\r\nThere are several uses not following Envoy type alias style.\r\nI've found those below so far.\r\n\r\n- `std::unique_ptr<ScopeKey>`\r\n- `std::unique_ptr<SnapshotImpl>`\r\n- `std::unique_ptr<NullVmPlugin>`\r\n- `std::unique_ptr<Configuration::FilterChainFactoryContext>`\r\n- `std::unique_ptr<NullVmPlugin>`\r\n- `std::shared_ptr<Network::DrainableFilterChain>`\r\n- `std::shared_ptr<FilterState>`\r\n- `std::shared_ptr<const Snapshot>`\r\n- `std::shared_ptr<GoogleStub>`\r\n\r\nThose are to be modified manually or something else?\r\n\r\nRelated #9840",
